  is: editable minecraft spell
  title: "Cyrus Spell to build Pyramids"
  Rules: uid-320d-55ec-ca58-8f71 uid-77a8-38ec-e0bc-b5f1 uid-df7c-2043-f410-724f uid-4506-0c41-ac8e-4084 uid-f363-ddd9-4da2-4c73
